<longTitle>
<docTitle class="centered fontsize12" style="-uslm-lc:I658005">An Act</docTitle>
<officialTitle class="indentUp0 firstIndent1 fontsize8" style="-uslm-lc:I658011">To extend the Alaska Native Vietnam era veterans land allotment program, and for other purposes.<sidenote><p class="centered fontsize8" id="x4fd0b06d-efd3-11f0-b6da-5f2d2070469d" style="-uslm-lc:I658076"><approvedDate date="2025-12-26">Dec. 26, 2025</approvedDate></p><p class="centered fontsize8" id="x4fd0b06e-efd3-11f0-b6da-5f2d2070469d" style="-uslm-lc:I658076">[<ref href="/us/bill/119/hr/410">H.R. 410</ref>]<?GPOvSpace 08?></p></sidenote></officialTitle>
</longTitle>
<enactingFormula style="-uslm-lc:I658120"><i>  Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representa­tives of the United States of America in Congress assembled,</i></enactingFormula><sidenote><p class="leftAlign firstIndent0 fontsize8" id="x4fd0b06f-efd3-11f0-b6da-5f2d2070469d" style="-uslm-lc:I658180">Alaska Native Vietnam Era Veterans Land Allotment Extension Act of 2025.</p></sidenote>
<section id="d659e88" identifier="/us/pl/119/63/s1" style="-uslm-lc:I658146"><num class="bold" value="1">SECTION 1. </num><sidenote><p class="leftAlign firstIndent0 fontsize8" id="x4fd0b070-efd3-11f0-b6da-5f2d2070469d" style="-uslm-lc:I658180"><ref href="/us/usc/t43/s1601">43 USC 1601 note</ref>.</p></sidenote><heading>SHORT TITLE.</heading><content style="-uslm-lc:I658120">  This Act may be cited as the “<shortTitle role="act">Alaska Native Vietnam Era Veterans Land Allotment Extension Act of 2025</shortTitle>”.</content></section>
<section id="d659e103" identifier="/us/pl/119/63/s2" role="instruction" style="-uslm-lc:I658141"><num class="fontsize12" value="2">SEC. 2. </num><heading>EXTENSION OF THE ALASKA NATIVE VIETNAM ERA VETERANS LAND ALLOTMENT PROGRAM.</heading><content style="-uslm-lc:I658120">  Section 1119(b)(3)(B) of the John D. Dingell, Jr. Conservation, Management, and Recreation Act (<ref href="/us/usc/t43/s1629g–1/b/3/B">43 U.S.C. 1629g–1(b)(3)(B)</ref>) <amendingAction type="amend">is amended</amendingAction> by <amendingAction type="delete">striking</amendingAction> “<quotedText>5-year period</quotedText>” and <amendingAction type="insert">inserting</amendingAction> “<quotedText>10-year period</quotedText>”.</content></section>
<action>
<actionDescription style="-uslm-lc:I658030">Approved</actionDescription> <date date="2025-12-26">December 26, 2025</date>.</action>
